name: Nathan Cregut
body:
***

Current student studying _Computer Game Design_ and _Computer Science_ with a minor in _Mathematics_ and _The Center of Excellence in Computer Information Systems_ at **Dakota State University**.
I am in my third year with a cumulative GPA of 3.5 and expecting to graduate in _May of 2019_.
Within the last two years I have worked as the lead programmer as well as the project manager for various classes, working on game projects and coding projects.
Currently I work as a tutor for Computer Science and Math classes at DSU.
